However, when solving QF_AUFBV constraints (`src/tactic/smtlogics/qfaufbv_tactic.cpp`), Z3 will always call the `smt_tactic` after some preprocessing phases.  Is it possible to implement a bit-blasting based tactic for QF_AUFBV? 

